                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 219.) I produce a certifi<lb></lb>cate of Burt's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
